---
import Button from './Button.astro';
---
<section class="speed-module" aria-labelledby="speed-module-heading">
  <div class="container speed-module__inner">
    <div class="speed-module__media">
      <img
        class="speed-module__img speed-module__img--main"
        src="/brand_assets/insights/HP.webp"
        alt="Interlocking paths finding their way forward"
        width="677" height="585" loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>

    <div class="speed-module__copy">
      <span class="section-tag"><span class="tag-dot"></span>Speed to learning</span>
      <h2 class="speed-module__heading" id="speed-module-heading">
        From idea to working product in <em>weeks, not months.</em>
      </h2>
      <p class="speed-module__lede">
        Not speed for speed's sake. Speed to learning — getting something real in
        front of real customers early enough that being wrong is cheap, and failing
        forward together is the plan rather than the disaster.
      </p>
      <ul class="speed-module__points">
        <li>Working software in weeks — not a deck describing software</li>
        <li>Evidence from real users before the big spend</li>
        <li>Built on architecture that can grow, not a throwaway</li>
      </ul>
      <div class="speed-module__actions">
        <Button href="/weeks-not-months" label="See how it works" variant="primary" />
        <Button href="/insights/mvp-apps-in-weeks-not-months" label="Read the thinking" variant="secondary" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
